Program: Outlook
Title: Reforming Criminals in Venezuela
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbs9p
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Alberto Vollmer and the success of Venezuela's Project Alcatraz in reforming violent gang members. Also, the French man whose Ukranian farming dream turned into a nightmare. Youk Chhang on being tortured by the Khymer Rouge and his work at the Documentation Center of Cambodia. Recalling a trek through the Sinai Peninsula in 1982. Presenter: Heather Payton. Show less